Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you warn me before you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Care to explain, Fullmetal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Crowley, Colonel. He keeps coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I thought we had it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the stone. We have to find the stone, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be close. Let's track it down and destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got ideas, by all means, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say, Colonel, but you're gonna have to buy us a little more time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that'll make it three, you owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
